les:     1  (migration)\nEdited files:  3  (work-orders.ts, api.ts, TemplateDetail.tsx)\nTotal:         4 files touched\n```\n\nThe existing inheritance chain (`system → company → project → unit`) stays exactly as-is. The `sop_id` rides along with the template through every copy/freeze operation automatically because the existing `copyTemplatesToOrg()` and `assign-to-project` endpoints already copy all columns.\n\n**Want me to proceed with the migration file first?**"
